-------------|--------|---------------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------|\n| 🥇   | Lockout (Heretic) | S-Tier | 🔴🟠🟡🟡🟢 | Best overall: strongest material rendering, cinematic lighting, depth   |\n| 🥈   | Huihui            | A-Tier | 🔴🟠🟡🟡⚪ | Very clean and stable, great faces, slightly too balanced / soft        |\n| 🥉   | Josiefied         | B-Tier | 🔴🟠🟡⚪⚪ | Smooth and controlled, but lacks contrast and material realism          |\n| ❌   | BennyDaBall       | Trash  | 🔴⚪⚪⚪⚪ | Inconsistent, weak material response, unstable details                  |\n\n---\n\n## 🎯 Recommendation (Z-Image Turbo)\n\n- **Primary CLIP:** Lockout (Heretic)\n- **Secondary Option:** Huihui (for face stability)\n- **Avoid:** BennyDaBall (for this use case)\n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ Key Insight\n\nCLIP choice has a **major impact** on:\n- material realism (especially latex)\n- lighting behavior\n- overall image mood and depth\n\nThis matters **more than sampler tweaks** in most cases."],"color":"#223","bgcolor":"#335"},{"id":70,"type":"MarkdownNote","pos":[-860,-600],"size":[860,300],"flags":{},"order":6,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"properties":{},"widgets_values":["# 📊 Z-Image Turbo – Resolution Guide (RTX 2070 | 8GB VRAM)\n\n| Resolution     | Quality        | VRAM Load       | Speed           | Stability       | Recommendation |\n|----------------|----------------|-----------------|-----------------|-----------------|----------------|\n| 704 × 1056     | 🔴🟠🟡⚪⚪ | 🔴⚪⚪⚪⚪ | 🔴🟠🟡🟡🟢 | 🔴🟠🟡🟡🟢 | Speed / testing |\n| 768 × 1152     | 🔴🟠🟡🟡⚪ | 🔴🟠🟡⚪⚪ | 🔴🟠🟡🟡⚪ | 🔴🟠🟡🟡🟢 | ⭐ **BEST DEFAULT** |\n| 832 × 1248     | 🔴🟠🟡🟡🟢 | 🔴🟠🟡🟡⚪ | 🔴🟠🟡⚪⚪ | 🔴🟠🟡🟡⚪ | ⭐ **Quality sweet spot** |\n| 896 × 1344     | 🔴🟠🟡🟡🟢 | 🔴🟠🟡🟡🟡 | 🔴🟠⚪⚪⚪ | 🔴🟠🟡⚪⚪ | Detail / high-end |\n| 944 × 1408     | 🔴🟠🟡🟡🟢 | 🔴🟠🟠⚪⚪ | 🔴⚪⚪⚪⚪ | 🔴🟠⚪⚪⚪ | Limit / testing only |\n\n---\n\n## 🧠 Interpretation\n\n### 🟢 Quality\n- Z-Image Turbo scales well up to ~832–896  \n- Beyond that: minimal real gain → mostly overhead  \n\n### 🟡 VRAM Behavior (8GB)\n- Up to **768×1152** = stable  \n- **832×1248** = usually stable  \n- **896+** depends heavily on:\n  - LoRAs  \n  - batch size  \n  - sampler  \n  - workflow complexity  \n\n### 🔴 Critical Range\n- **944×1408**\n  - can work  \n  - but:\n    - slow  \n    - VRAM spikes  \n    - unstable in complex workflows  \n\n---\n\n## 🎯 Clear Recommendation\n\n- **Default:** `768 × 1152`  \n- **Best quality without stress:** `832 × 1248`  \n- **Maximum reasonable:** `896 × 1344`  \n- **Above that:** only for controlled testing  \n\n---\n\n## ⚠️ Bonus (relevant for your setup)\n\nFor try-on workflows:\n\n- Input resize: **~832**  \n- Output:\n  - stable: `768 × 1152`  \n  - high quality: `832 × 1248`  \n\n→ helps prevent:\n- mask drift  \n- outfit artifacts  \n- unnecessary VRAM issues  "],"color":"#223","bgcolor":"#335"},{"id":72,"type":"MarkdownNote","pos":[940,-600],"size":[840,440],"flags":{},"order":7,"mode":0,"inputs":[],"outputs":[],"properties":{},"widgets_values":["# Sampler and Scheduler Recommendations by Model Family\n\n> Rated on a visual scale: 🔴 poor → 🟢 optimal\n\n| Model Family | Sampler | Scheduler | Rating |\n|---|---|---|---|\n| **Z-Image Turbo** | dpmpp_sde | beta | 🔴🟠🟡🟡🟢 |\n|  | dpmpp_sde | ddim_uniform | 🔴🟠🟡🟡🟢 |\n|  | euler_ancestral | beta | 🔴🟠🟡🟡⚪ |\n|  | euler_ancestral | ddim_uniform | 🔴🟠🟡🟡⚪ |\n|  | dpmpp_sde | sgm_uniform | 🔴🟠🟡⚪⚪ |\n|  | euler_ancestral | sgm_uniform | 🔴🟠🟡⚪⚪ |\n|  | euler | beta | 🔴🟠⚪⚪⚪ |\n|  | euler | ddim_uniform | 🔴🟠⚪⚪⚪ |\n|  | euler | karras | 🔴⚪⚪⚪⚪ |\n| **Flux.2 Klein** | dpmpp_2m | sgm_uniform | 🔴🟠🟡🟡🟢 |\n|  | dpmpp_sde | sgm_uniform | 🔴🟠🟡🟡⚪ |\n|  | dpmpp_2m | beta | 🔴🟠🟡🟡⚪ |\n|  | euler | simple | 🔴🟠🟡⚪⚪ |\n|  | euler | beta | 🔴🟠🟡⚪⚪ |\n|  | euler | ddim_uniform | 🔴🟠⚪⚪⚪ |\n|  | euler_ancestral | sgm_uniform | 🔴🟠⚪⚪⚪ |\n|  | dpmpp_sde | beta | 🔴🟠⚪⚪⚪ |\n|  | euler | karras | 🔴⚪⚪⚪⚪ |\n| **Qwen (Diffusion)** | dpmpp_sde | beta | 🔴🟠🟡🟡🟢 |\n|  | dpmpp_2m | sgm_uniform | 🔴🟠🟡🟡🟢 |\n|  | dpmpp_sde | sgm_uniform | 🔴🟠🟡🟡⚪ |\n|  | d